fo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2178416778","tinyui":"/x/igDYgQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2178416778","webui":"/spaces/BAN/overview","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2178416778"}},{"id":"4598988840","type":"folder","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:folder/activation/3feb9026-40ef-4a53-9bfd-75d0dc16e0f6/4598988840","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmZvbGRlci9hY3RpdmF0aW9uLzNmZWI5MDI2LTQwZWYtNGE1My05YmZkLTc1ZDBkYzE2ZTBmNi80NTk4OTg4ODQw","status":"current","title":"Rails Seriaframework","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":887958739},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/4598988840/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/4598988840/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/4598988840/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/4598988840/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/4598988840","editui":"/spaces/BAN/folder/4598988840","webui":"/spaces/BAN/folder/4598988840","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/folder/4598988840"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<p local-id=\"31b110c6-2d83-44e9-8263-b6ddee6cf7be\">Lista de requerimientos para el seriaframework:</p><ul local-id=\"a67bec29-0e38-4eee-99bb-21353a878dfe\"><li local-id=\"10436ffe-f163-472c-b840-32771f1bfa33\"><p local-id=\"14b0f0e3-d17e-44fa-aa4f-e40bb0877bd9\">Serializaci&oacute;n</p></li><li local-id=\"0f1da260-89df-47a8-a11c-951690409863\"><p local-id=\"c2f23355-f238-4b82-a091-84f2a639e609\">Manejo de errores y messages, probablemente en un middleware o explorar el rescue_from de rails (no me acuerdo como lo hice en pix)</p></li><li local-id=\"fe2c9715-b6a7-4995-b01b-10d1843e736a\"><p local-id=\"5acaccbf-7afc-49d4-bed5-7dfe06e65bc9\">Par&aacute;metros opcionales de respuesta</p></li><li local-id=\"fe2c9715-b6a7-4995-b01b-10d1843e736a\"><p local-id=\"5acaccbf-7afc-49d4-bed5-7dfe06e65bc9\">respuestas dinamicas? type: object</p></li><li local-id=\"4df88118-6d49-46fb-84f2-48cfc90f37b7\"><p local-id=\"cd0c166f-12bc-4a26-8d3a-852fe98d9ee1\">Clases y excepciones dentro del namespace de la gema</p></li><li local-id=\"1ec52cb9-aaaa-4370-842a-26963d3da7fa\"><p local-id=\"539f3737-1de5-47fe-94f5-85cc59c6eadc\">Ser&iacute;a bueno que en la documentaci&oacute;n no obligue a pasar una &ldquo;master&ldquo; key para dentro devolver el objeto. Que permita devolver la representation de un objeto directamente en el root de la respuesta.</p></li><li local-id=\"f04bc6bc-fe52-44fb-929d-5915b664b71e\"><p local-id=\"7546ad0b-48a7-4dcb-9ef5-6cf0fd59622d\">Ser un contrato a todas las respuestas de la API (Que la respuesta de la API sea la misma que est&aacute; definida en la doc)</p></li></ul><p local-id=\"e020543b-1f33-466f-a1b5-9c653269af0c\" /><ul local-id=\"d1388a07-29e5-4488-bb2c-6f8d7334c200\"><li local-id=\"9772a782-786b-4141-a344-766fbb699250\"><p local-id=\"5c52ada6-404c-430c-8be1-b97c5f2c44aa\">En principio vamos a ir por definir la informaci&oacute;n de las operaciones en el routes.rb definiendo los atributos custom de las rutas.</p></li><li local-id=\"19168122-a0e6-4e25-aacf-990e9c806a77\"><p local-id=\"c7d59744-5609-4dd1-8f0d-58beb1cc0e64\">Revisar como se usa jbuilder, la idea es replicar un poco su funcionamiento, usando el archivo que est&eacute; dentro de las views y usando partials para reutilizar.</p></li><li local-id=\"a45936dd-16a3-404f-bb19-c2acc658fabf\"><p local-id=\"8ba275b6-571d-4fd0-87e5-73acabbb617a\">Ver la posibilidad de poder anidar campos en la respuesta sin la necesidad de usar partials/representations.</p></li></ul><p local-id=\"2a18d5b9-5349-4736-aea2-50dc64d073b2\" /><ul local-id=\"e6125bd3-a991-4526-a3ba-ae283457e07f\"><li local-id=\"a80f241c-ced7-400e-a9a6-b8b419fdd631\"><p local-id=\"34498abf-094c-4ed7-8b5c-8910563203a6\">Falta ver lo de los par&aacute;metros de entrada. Como vamos a hacer para documentarlos?</p></li><li local-id=\"ada92b40-6a65-4cb5-9b7b-22dedf917aa3\"><p local-id=\"1f9239ad-f33c-48eb-b47a-144a2f5cdde0\">Definir la url de la documentaci&oacute;n &ldquo;/doc&rdquo;, y exponerla (En principio como una ruta est&aacute;tica, no como parte del routes.rb)</p></li></ul><p local-id=\"66328e5d-8cbd-497f-a570-96a7c42b3061\" />","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/4601315348"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":672},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/4601315348/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/4601315348/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/4601315348/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/4601315348/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/4601315348/Requerimientos+del+SeriaFramework","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/4601315348/Requerimientos+del+SeriaFramework","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/4601315348/Requerimientos+del+SeriaFramework","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/4601315348","tinyui":"/x/FIBCEgE","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}